{
  "texts": [
    "Most catalogues (92%) provide at least a web search GUI.",
    "The non-SPARQL catalogues represent 61% (16) of the total; around 88% of these use a web search GUI, and 56% combine it with REST APIs.",
    "Therefore, only 10 out of 26 provide a SPARQL endpoint.",
    "70% of these provide machine-readable metadata.",
    "Overall, the preferred technology used by all the catalogues integrating machine-readable metadata is either REST APIs, web search GUI, or both."
  ]
}